data.description:
Discover your dream home in The Woodlands Hills! Brick, stone, & stucco exteriors exude elegance. Flooring throughout entry, living, dining and kitchen has been modified to enhance the modern look by using vinyl and tile. The kitchen attributes stainless steel appliances, reverse osmosis, & an AQUASANA water softener while opening up to spacious family room with tall ceilings & dining area with a wall of windows. This split floor plan makes it easy to study or work from home, as the office is tucked away. A TRUE 3-car garage boasts epoxy floors- 20 amp/GFCI outlets & plumbing for power-washer. Lushly landscaped yard surrounds the wide, extended driveway. Gate access on both sides of fence with backyard garage entry, & exterior electrical outlets add convenience. A gas line under covered patio & electrical outlets placed above for TV. They thought of it all! Hardware spruce up cabinets, while 2-inch blinds throughout, WASHER/ DRYER/ REFRIGERATOR INCLUDED
